41349 臺中市霧峰區吉峰東路168號 朝陽科技大學-語言中心 Language Center, Chaoyang University of Technology 
    Location：Design Building 2F(D-208) Opening Hours: Mon. to Fri. 8:00 A.M - 07:00 P.M. 
    Tel：(04) 2332-3000 EXT 7522~7525 E-mail：flc@cyut.edu.tw(Foreign Language Section) cl@cyut.edu.tw (Chinese Learning Section) 瀏覽人次：757398





















